translation[13]{c,v,t}:
  35,45,Aur agar Allah Taalaa logon per unn kay aemaal kay sabab darogeer farmaney lagta to roy-e-zamin per aik jaandaar ko na chorta lekin Allah Taalaa inn ko aik miyad-e-moyyan tak mohlat dey raha hai so jab inn ki woh miyad aa phonchay gi Allah Taalaa apnay bandon ko aap dekh ley ga
  36,1,Yaseen
  36,2,Qasam hai quran ba-hikmat ki
  36,3,Kay be-shak aap payghumbaron mein hain
  36,4,Seedhay rastay per hain
  36,5,Yeh quran Allah zabardast meharban ki taraf say nazil kiya gaya hai
  36,6,Takay aap aisay logon ko darayen jin kay baap daday nahi daraye gaye thay so (issi waja say) yeh ghafil hain
  36,7,Inn mein say aksar logon per baat sabit hochuki hai so yeh log eman na layen gay
  36,8,Hum ney unn ki gardano mein toq daal diyey hain phir woh thoriyon tak hain jiss say unn kay sir uper ko ulat gaye hain
  36,9,Aur hum ney aik aarh unn kay samney ker di aur aik aarh unn kay peechay kerdi jiss say hum ney unn ko dhank diya so woh nahi dekh saktay
  36,10,Aur aap inn ko darayen ya na darayen dono barabar hain yeh eman nahi layen gay
  36,11,Bus aap to sirf aisay shaks ko dara saktay hain jo naseehat per chalay aur rehman say bey dekhay daray so aap uss ko maghfirat aur baq-waqar ajar ki khushkhabriyan suna dijiyey
  36,12,Be-shak hum murdon ko zindah keren gay aur hum likhtay jatay hain woh aemaal bhi jin ko log aagay bhejtay hain aur unn kay woh aemaal bhi jin ko peechay chor jatay hain aur hum ney her cheez ko aik wazeh kitab mein zabt ker rakha hai